{"tid":694761,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥 隻Game到底搞成點","createTime":"2018-06-08T15:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T11:40:29.000Z","uid":5834,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa52939a4c940f6e355638b464ae4a31d9854ac","tid":694761,"uid":5834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:09:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩法國 重有廿幾日就已經一年<br />\n話說上年6月尾 tat無啦啦做左遊戲公司CEO 然後搞左個發佈會 話要2022入亞運 同應該俾佢做電競局長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/TouchFun/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FTouchFun%2F&d=E4ILr%2BITO37y6XHO142KSb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6a7e0356\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/TouchFun/</a><br />\n間公司到依家成年 可以話0消息 個fb page整完又咩都冇放上去除左發佈會果日既相<br />\n<br />\n果800萬投資開發隻遊戲 到底依家咩環境<br />\n就算係之前tat買左版權再配音果隻三國舊game AppStore 公司名都係用返達哥自己undergroundv 而唔係800萬果間 達魂制作Touchfun<br />\n<br />\n同埋都係見達哥好似同之前一樣自己接job廣告 出席下活動咁 但全部都同上年做CEO 開發game無關 又無提下點<br />\n之前佢開台好似有話咩幾個月後 但依家都過哂 又係無消息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底搞咩<br />\n<br />\n利申： 撐達哥架我"},{"pid":"347ade19c7e34581735bb6a90d6a98d2d3dae017","tid":694761,"uid":102589,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"蝕到傻咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc070aaa0a214bfb938165ca11c85898d5971e9c","tid":694761,"uid":14602,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"蝕錢咪要做其他野幫補下lo"},{"pid":"18dbe76ea147c797878945dd0b1e3387fb2271d0","tid":694761,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:14:59.000Z","msg":"隻野太柒 幫佢唔到"},{"pid":"1bad2ef38c5308928687c7094d551dae3b90d956","tid":694761,"uid":5834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"347ade19c7e34581735bb6a90d6a98d2d3dae017","tid":694761,"uid":102589,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyT